  "Why not make clustering the primary method?", "The project requirement centers on supervised prediction of an outcome. Clustering is more useful as a supporting segmentation method.",
  "Potential future use", "Create student-support personas such as attendance-risk, financial-risk, engagement-risk, or high-support-usage groups."
)

